[ Modifiers ] 

Mod 1												Modifier key - Alt Left Key
Mod 4												Windows key - 'Win' Logo Key

[ Bindings ]

[ Bar ]

Modifier											Show bar

[ Cheat Sheet ]

Modifier + Shift + ~								Show cheat sheet 

[ Background ]

Modifier + G										Change back[g]round image 

[ Launcher ]

Modifier + Space									Open launcher 

[ Terminal ]

Modifier + T										Open [t]erminal

[ Kill Switch ]

Modifier + Shift+ K										Kill application instance 

[ Window Focus ]

Modifier + Up										Change focus [up]
Modifier + Left										Change focus [left]
Modifier + Down										Change focus [down]
Modifier + Right									Change focus [right]

[ Window Move]

Modifier + Shift + Up								Move focused window [up]
Modifier + Shift + Left								Move focused window [left]
Modifier + Shift + Down								Move focused window [down]
Modifier + Shift + Right							Move focused window [right]

[ Window Layout ]

Modifier + H										Split [h]orizontal - vertical layout
Modifier + V										Split [v]ertical   - horizontal layout

Modifier + W										Toggle floating windows
Modifier + F										Toggle fullscreen windows

[ Container Layout ]

Modifier + S										Change container layout  - [s]plit
Modifier + K										Change container layout  - stac[k]
Modifier + B										Change container layout  - ta[b]

Modifier + Shift + W								Change [w]indow focus - tiling / floating

Modifier + P										Focus [p]arent container
Modifier + C										Focus [c]hild container

Modifier + Shift + A								Move floating container to the [a]bsolute center
Modifier + Shift + M								Move container to the current [m]ouse cursor position

[ Workspaces ]

Modifier + 1										Switch to workspace [1]
Modifier + 2										Switch to workspace [2]
Modifier + 3										Switch to workspace [3]
Modifier + 4										Switch to workspace [4]
Modifier + 5										Switch to workspace [5]
Modifier + 6										Switch to workspace [6]
Modifier + 7										Switch to workspace [7]
Modifier + 8										Switch to workspace [8]

Modifier + Shift + 1								Move container to workspace number [1]
Modifier + Shift + 2								Move container to workspace number [2]
Modifier + Shift + 3								Move container to workspace number [3]
Modifier + Shift + 4								Move container to workspace number [4]
Modifier + Shift + 5								Move container to workspace number [5]
Modifier + Shift + 6								Move container to workspace number [6]
Modifier + Shift + 7								Move container to workspace number [7]
Modifier + Shift + 8								Move container to workspace number [8]

[ Resize Mode ]

Modifier + Z										Enter resi[z]e mode

	Modifier + Shift + Z							Resize - reset window width and height to configured size
	Left											Resize - shrink window width by 10 px
	Up												Resize - shrink window height by 10 px
	Down											Resize - grow window height by 10 px
	Right											Resize - grow window width by 10 px

Modifier + Z										Exit resize mode

Modifier + R										[R]eload i3 configuration
Modifier + Shift + R								[R]estart i3

Modifier + Shift + X								E[x]it i3